canUnifyWith

public boolean canUnifyWith(Atom p)
i think this is no real unification routine because the variable values are not available. So, it's rather a raw check to see if 2 preds CAN eventually unify (??) (foo bar) unifies with (foo ?x) (foo ?x) unifies with (foo ?y) (foo bar) does NOT unify with (foo some) (foo bar ?x) unifies with (foo bar ?y) (foo bar ?x) does NOT unify with (foo run ?y)
